      "body" : "I've just introduced this to Alpine Linux. The bitcoin daemon runs under /var/lib/bitcoin as bitcoin:bitcoin using /etc/bitcoin.conf for configuration. The post install script generates a random user / pass / port for a new installation. The init script also enforces sensible permissions.\r\n\r\nVia LXC 1.00+ it is possible to run an unprivileged Alpine container on any Linux (size 5mb)\r\n\r\nSame is possible for namecoin ",
