      "body" : "This (and PR #4611) is some nice work. Is there any (official) effort to make an Ubuntu (or other distro) package that includes it?\r\n\r\n(Edit: I've seen the existing PPA repository and the current bitcoin package does not include any init scripts)\r\n",
