   {
      "body" : "On any Linux distribution install [LXC](https://linuxcontainers.org/) (Ubuntu / Debian / Redhat / Archlinux / OpenSUSE have packages) & create an [Alpine Linux container](http://wiki.alpinelinux.org/wiki/LXC) (this is 5 meg in size).\r\n\r\nLog in to the container (user = root & password is empty) & run:\r\n\r\n    apk add bitcoin\r\n    rc-update add bitcoin default\r\n    rc-service bitcoin start\r\n\r\n& bitcoin will run as user bitcoin. There is also a package for namecoin in Alpine.\r\n\r\nFor extra security & complete isolation run an [unprivileged container](http://www.stgraber.org/2014/01/17/lxc-1-0-unprivileged-containers/).\r\n\r\n[Ubuntu docs for LXC](https://help.ubuntu.com/12.04/serverguide/lxc.html)",
      "created_at" : "2014-09-17T01:25:42Z",
